02:01.120 --> 02:04.271
<i>I have a girlfriend whom</i>
<i>I neither manage nor service.</i>

02:04.360 --> 02:07.830
<i>That's my best friend, Barry,</i>
<i>fucking her on an IKEA kitchen table</i>

02:07.920 --> 02:10.434
<i>I picked up for a really good price.</i>

02:12.280 --> 02:15.670
<i>I'm finding it hard to care about</i>
<i>anything these days.</i>

02:15.760 --> 02:20.788
<i>In fact, the only thing I do care about</i>
<i>is the fact that I can't care about anything.</i>

02:20.880 --> 02:22.518
<i>Seriously. It worries me.</i>

02:24.160 --> 02:26.390
<i>My name is Wesley Gibson.</i>

02:30.480 --> 02:33.711
<i>My dad walked out on my mom</i>
<i>when I was seven days old.</i>

02:33.800 --> 02:38.351
<i>Sometimes I wonder if he ever looked</i>
<i>into my baby blues eyes and asked himself,</i>

02:39.320 --> 02:43.950
<i>"Did I just father the most insignificant</i>
<i>asshole of the 21st century?"</i>

02:58.840 --> 03:02.992
Well, if you could get me the consignment
to me by the 28th... Yeah.

03:03.680 --> 03:06.399
Do you have the numbers in front of you?

03:17.000 --> 03:18.149
Relax.

03:18.240 --> 03:21.232
If your name had come up,
you'd be dead already.

03:23.800 --> 03:26.678
We've had some unexpected losses recently.

03:28.240 --> 03:30.037
We'd like to know

03:30.120 --> 03:32.918
